    partners and volunteers. You agree not to use the site to distribute malicious code, attempt to
    compromise its security, or misuse it in any way that disrupts the experience for others.
  </p>

  <h2>Donations</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>All donations are voluntary and generally non-refundable.</li>
    <li>Online donations are processed securely by PayPal, subject to PayPal's terms.</li>
    <li>Expedition Reading is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit; donations are tax-deductible to the fullest extent allowed by law.</li>
    <li>If you believe a donation was made in error, email us within seven days and we will work with you on the appropriate remedy.</li>
